1. Core Philosophy
Privacy First
We do not collect your data. Period. Every piece of information remains exclusively within your browser's local storage â€” never transmitted, never exposed.
Serverless Architecture
With no backend servers, there is zero risk of data breaches. Postrix responds instantly, regardless of your internet connection status.
Pure Web Technology
Built entirely with HTML, CSS, and JavaScript â€” no unnecessary libraries, no bloated frameworks. Postrix is engineered to be exceptionally lightweight, ensuring zero impact on your browser's performance.

2. Workspace Management: Auto Mode & Pin
Postrix intelligently recognizes the pages you visit and manages your workspace accordingly.
ğŸ“ Auto Workspace (Auto Mode)
When visiting a standard website, Postrix analyzes the URL and automatically loads the widgets associated with that page. Resume exactly where you left off â€” no configuration required.
ğŸ“Œ Pin Current Page â€” Highly Recommended
Websites built on SPA (Single Page Application) frameworks â€” such as YouTube or Gmail â€” dynamically update URLs without full page reloads, which can interfere with automatic workspace detection.
Solution: Use the "Pin Current Page" button to assign a name and anchor your workspace to a specific page. This manually created workspace acts as a stable anchor, ensuring your widgets remain intact even as the URL shifts.
Additionally, you can create multiple pins within a single site â€” for example, separating "Work" and "Study" workspaces â€” and switch between widget sets seamlessly.

