5. Technical Notes
Live Widget Limitations
Live Widgets, which retrieve real-time data, perform optimally on static page structures. On SPA-based sites such as YouTube, real-time data tracking may be limited. In such cases, we recommend utilizing standard Memo or Checklist widgets as alternatives.
Data Deletion Warning
The "Delete All Data" function permanently removes all Postrix data stored in your browser. As no server-side backup exists, please proceed with caution.

6. Data Management
Active
Displays all widgets currently associated with the active page or pin.
Storage
A secure holding area for widgets you don't need on-screen right now, but may wish to retrieve later.
Trash
Deleted widgets are moved here. Restore or permanently delete them at any time.
